## search engines:
searchengine googlessl https://www.google.com/search?q=%s
searchengine google http://www.google.com/search?q=%s
searchengine images http://www.google.com/images?q=%s&um=1&ie=UTF-8&source=og&sa=N&hl=en&tab=wi
searchengine wikipedia https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/w/index.php?search=%s
searchengine wikipedias https://secure.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/w/index.php?search=%s
searchengine bbs https://bbs.archlinux.org/search.php?action=search&keywords=%s&author=&forum=-1&search_in=all&sort_by=0&sort_dir=DESC&show_as=topics
searchengine github https://github.com/search?q=%s&type=Everything&repo=&langOverride=&start_value=1
searchengine newegg http://www.newegg.com/Product/ProductList.aspx?Submit=ENE&DEPA=0&Order=BESTMATCH&Description=%s
searchengine tigerdirect http://www.tigerdirect.com/applications/SearchTools/search.asp?keywords=%s
searchengine imdb http://www.imdb.com/find?s=all&q=%s
searchengine youtube http://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s
searchengine deviantart http://browse.deviantart.com/?qh=&section=&global=1&q=%s
searchengine lastfm http://www.last.fm/music/?q=%s
searchengine amazon http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=nb_ss_gw?url=search-alias%3Dall&field-keywords=%s
searchengine ebay http://shop.ebay.com/?_from=R40&_trksid=p3907.m570.l1313&_nkw=%s&_sacat=See-All-Categories
searchengine kickass http://www.kickasstorrents.com/search/%s/
